  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>With its first class service and top cuisine the Hotel Arlberg enjoys an excellent reputation around the world. Located in a prime position in <a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech">Lech</a>  </span><span>opposite</span><span> the main ski lifts and in the heart of the village.</span> </p>
<h2>Ski in, ski out</h2>
<p><span>Sitting discreetly back from the road, the hotel is set in the heart of village life. </span>You can easily explore the boutiques, cafes and shops of Lech right on your doorstep from this prime location.</p>
<p><span>Set opposite the main ski lifts it is possible to ski to and from the hotel door.</span></p>
<h2><span>Warm welcome</span></h2>
<p><span>Despite the modest guest house being one of the leading five star hotels in Lech, the Arlberg is still the Schneider's family home to this day. They believe in the lore of hospitality and traditions and nothing is too much trouble for their dedicated staff.</span></p>
<h2><span>Outdoor pool with views</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel recently unveiled an outdoor pool with unrivalled views of the Arlberg mountain. The wellness facilities also include an 11 metre indoor pool, multiple saunas, and experience &amp; sensory showers.</span></p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Arlberg making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
