  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Austrian Twins</strong> are around 25m² and can sleep up to three (single sofa bed). These rooms have a shower and a seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Austrian Twins</strong> are around 35m² and have both bath and shower, and a lounge area with a single sofa bed that can sleep a third guest. These rooms are on request from January so please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are around 55m² and sleep up to four. These spacious rooms are on request from January so please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> at 18m² are also available with a shower.</p>
